snippet.title: Prison Boss: Prohibition - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: Here's your look at the announcement trailer for Prison Boss: Prohibition, an upcoming co-op crafting, trading, and simulation VR game. In Prison Boss: Prohibition, run various shops throughout New Yolk City, producing and selling merchandise that's both strictly legal and questionably not, all to get super duper rich! Prison Boss: Prohibition will be available on PS VR2, Meta Quest, and Steam VR. The Open Alpha for Prison Boss: Prohibition begins on October 9, 2024.
